snippet.title: Twinsanity: Omicron - Launch Trailer | PC, Android
snippet.description:
THE STORY CONTINUES!
One week left to the release of the game!
Twinsanity is back in his timeline after defeating Time Shadow and taking his Relic of Time. But this is not where the evil ends. Two days after the events of “Trapped in Time”, Twinsanity figures out that someone wants his power. Who? How? Why? 

If you like this trailer press the "Like" button and subscribe to my channel for more awesome videos. 

Check my Instagram for more upcoming episodes:
twinsanity_s_channel
